	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego vicissim quoque pauca scribo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae de pace habeo, mitto ad fratrem; is ea tibi communicabit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Unum hoc excidit, quod ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2478" cert="high">Sabaudum</placeName>, <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevenses</placeName> nullam habere spem, quod recepturus sit pacem illam constitutam et factam nuper in conventu Neodunensi, cui consul etiam vester interfuit; gravat enim illos novis de novo exactionibus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cuius rei gratia his diebus legationem huc miserunt, et nostri scribunt pro illis ad ducem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Arbitrantur multi,</foreign> es werd gon wie vornaher: des läbens werd kein end sin, bis man wider mitt dem paner dran muͤß.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">A <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> iam nihil habeo; cum accepero aliquid, communicabo tibi.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reliqua in fratris literis continentur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te novus consul noster dominus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3659">a Mülinen</persName>, vetus itam d. <persName ref="p8063" cert="high">Steigerus</persName>, qui, licet ambulare possit, adhuc tamen se domi continet, quia non audet adhuc se sine baculo aut sustentaculo itineri committere.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat item te <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high">Blasius</persName>, gener meus, qui iam hic mecum est, socer item, <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p3494">Diesbachius</persName> quoque et <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p7511">Gravenrietus</persName> cum <persName type="citizen_name">Manuele</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 22. aprilis 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Remitto ea, quę <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> ad te missa sunt, et ago tibi pro his gratias.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te etiam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20327" cert="high">Io[hannes] Iac[obus] Bonstetterus</persName>, gubernator <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l339" cert="high">Neocomensis</placeName>, singulariter.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[ohannes] Hallerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
